<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <style>
        body {{
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }}

        .email-container {{
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            border-radius: 8px;
            overflow: hidden;
        }}

        .header {{
            background-color: #394459;
            color: #ffffff;
            padding: 20px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            position: relative;
        }}

        .header h1 {{
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 24px;
        }}

        .content {{
            padding: 20px;
            color: #333333;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }}

        .content h2 {{
            font-size: 20px;
            margin-top: 0;
            color: #488099;
        }}

        .content p {{
            margin: 10px 0;
        }}

        .content a {{
            color: #488099;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: bold;
        }}

        .content a:hover {{
            text-decoration: underline;
        }}

        .footer {{
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            color: #666;
            font-size: 12px;
        }}

        .footer a {{
            color: #90c37f;
            text-decoration: none;
        }}

        .emoji {{
            font-size: 1.2em;
        }}

        .info-box {{
            background-color: #fff8e0;
            border-left: 4px solid #394459;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 15px 0;
            border-radius: 4px;
        }}

        .code {{
            background-color: #f5f5f5;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            border-radius: 3px;
            padding: 2px 4px;
            font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace;
            font-size: 0.9em;
            color: #333;
        }}

        .details-list {{
            margin: 15px 0;
        }}

        .details-list li {{
            margin: 8px 0;
        }}

        @media (max-width: 600px) {{
            .content h2 {{
                font-size: 18px;
            }}

            .header h1 {{
                font-size: 20px;
            }}
        }}
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="email-container">
        <div class="header">
            <center>
            <img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/evidencepub/brand/main/logo/png/white_300x300.png" style="height: 50px; display:block;">
            </center>
        </div>

        <div class="content">
            <h2>PREVIEW Build Started</h2>

            <p>We're weaving your <strong>{owner_name}/{repo_name}</strong> preprint into existence...</p>

            <div class="info-box">
                <p><strong>Build Details:</strong></p>
                <ul class="details-list">
                    <li><strong>Task ID:</strong> <span class="code">{task_id}</span></li>
                    <li><strong>Commit Hash:</strong> <span class="code">{commit_hash}</span></li>
                    <li><strong>Binder Hash:</strong> <span class="code">{binder_hash}</span></li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <p>You will receive another notification once the build is completed. Please allow some time for the process to finish.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>Thank you for using our MyST build service!</p>
            <center>
            <img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/evidencepub/brand/main/logo/png/colored_300x300.png" style="height: 25px; display:block;">
            </center>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>